## TIPS FOR INTERVIEW SUCCESS
==========================================

✓ PREPARATION
- Practice coding on whiteboard/online judges (LeetCode, HackerRank)
- Understand time & space complexity
- Be ready to optimize solutions
- Practice system design discussions

✓ DURING INTERVIEW
- Clarify requirements before jumping to solutions
- Think out loud - explain your reasoning
- Ask follow-up questions
- Discuss trade-offs
- Test your code mentally
- Discuss complexity with interviewer

✓ BEHAVIORAL
- Use STAR method for all stories
- Focus on YOUR contribution
- Mention collaboration and teamwork
- Show learning and growth mindset
- Have questions for interviewer about role/company

✓ COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID
- Not understanding problem completely
- Jumping to solution without analysis
- Not discussing trade-offs
- Writing code without testing
- Not considering edge cases
- Poor communication
- Negative attitude about past experiences

